                            <comment id="166093" author="gerrit" created="Wed, 14 Sep 2016 23:50:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andreas Dilger (andreas.dilger@intel.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/17634/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/17634/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-314&quot; title=&quot;Create additions to the Lustre manual for IU&amp;#39;s nodemap feature.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUDOC-314&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUDOC-314&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; nodemap: first commit of nodemap documentation&lt;br/&gt;
